                <h2>Paragon Board Order</h2>
                <p>Attach boards in this order. Route through nodes that give Intelligence, Minion Damage, and damage reduction. Socket the listed Glyph in each board's Glyph socket once it reaches level 15.</p>

                <div class="paragon-board">
