                    <p style="color: #c0c0c0; margin: 0;">Glyph: <span class="glyph-name">Sacrifice</span></p>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px;">Sacrifice glyph increases damage per sacrificed minion type. With Mages sacrificed, this provides a solid damage boost. Route toward Rare nodes that grant minion damage and damage reduction.</p>
