                    </div>
                    <p style="color: #c0c0c0; margin: 0;">Glyph: <span class="glyph-name">Hulking</span></p>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px;">Hulking glyph increases Golem damage and grants damage reduction per active minion. With three golems and warriors, this is a massive boost. Scent of Death board provides corpse consumption bonuses that synergize with Corpse Explosion.</p>
