                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px;">Essence glyph increases damage based on current Essence. With Deathspeaker's Pendant generating Blood Surge constantly, you maintain high Essence. This board provides life and damage nodes for mid-game survivability.</p>
