                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px;">Gravekeeper grants bonus damage after consuming a corpse. With constant Corpse Explosion usage, this buff is permanently active. Wither board has Legendary nodes that boost Shadow damage, scaling Corpse Explosion bursts.</p>
